        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8466",
        "content": "\"I have sinned-c'est vrai-but, my good sir, consider!--you have no actual intention of putting such-such barbarous threats into execution.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
