        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8466/274557/8466_274557_000015_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8466",
        "content": "Astarte!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8466_274557_000015_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8466/274557/8466_274557_000015_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8466",
        "content": "Astoreth!--a thousand and the same! And Rafaelle has beheld them!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8466_274557_000015_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8466/274557/8466_274557_000015_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8466",
        "content": "Yes, Rafaelle has been here, for did he not paint the-? and was he not consequently damned?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
