    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8466_274557_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8466/274557/8466_274557_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8466",
        "content": "His Majesty looked chagrined.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8466_285142_000001_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8466/285142/8466_285142_000001_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8466",
        "content": "Almost every devout admirer of the old bards, if demanded his opinion of their productions, would mention vaguely, yet with perfect sincerity, a sense of dreamy, wild, indefinite, and he would perhaps say, indefinable delight; on being required to point out the source of this so shadowy pleasure, he would be apt to speak of the quaint in phraseology and in general handling.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8466_285142_000001_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8466/285142/8466_285142_000001_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8466",
        "content": "This quaintness is, in fact, a very powerful adjunct to ideality, but in the case in question it arises independently of the author's will, and is altogether apart from his intention.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8466_285142_000001_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8466/285142/8466_285142_000001_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8466",
        "content": "Words and their rhythm have varied.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8466_285142_000001_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8466/285142/8466_285142_000001_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8466",
        "content": "Verses which affect us to day with a vivid delight, and which delight, in many instances, may be traced to the one source, quaintness, must have worn in the days of their construction, a very commonplace air.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8466_285142_000001_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8466/285142/8466_285142_000001_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8466",
        "content": "No general error evinces a more thorough confusion of ideas than the error of supposing Donne and Cowley metaphysical in the sense wherein Wordsworth and Coleridge are so.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8466_285142_000001_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8466/285142/8466_285142_000001_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8466",
        "content": "With the two former ethics were the end with the two latter the means.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8466_285142_000001_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8466/285142/8466_285142_000001_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8466",
        "content": "The poet of the \"Creation\" wished, by highly artificial verse, to inculcate what he supposed to be moral truth the poet of the \"Ancient Mariner\" to infuse the Poetic Sentiment through channels suggested by analysis.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8466_285142_000001_000010",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8466/285142/8466_285142_000001_000010.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8466",
        "content": "The one finished by complete failure what he commenced in the grossest misconception; the other, by a path which could not possibly lead him astray, arrived at a triumph which is not the less glorious because hidden from the profane eyes of the multitude.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8466_285142_000001_000011",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8466/285142/8466_285142_000001_000011.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8466",
        "content": "But in this view even the \"metaphysical verse\" of Cowley is but evidence of the simplicity and single heartedness of the man.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8466_285142_000001_000012",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8466/285142/8466_285142_000001_000012.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8466",
        "content": "And he was in this but a type of his school for we may as well designate in this way the entire class of writers whose poems are bound up in the volume before us, and throughout all of whom there runs a very perceptible general character.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8466_285142_000001_000013",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8466/285142/8466_285142_000001_000013.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8466",
        "content": "They used little art in composition. Their writings sprang immediately from the soul and partook intensely of that soul's nature.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8466_285142_000002_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8466/285142/8466_285142_000002_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8466",
        "content": "We can not bring ourselves to believe that the selections of the \"Book of Gems\" are such as will impart to a poetical reader the clearest possible idea of the beauty of the school but if the intention had been merely to show the school's character, the attempt might have been considered successful in the highest degree.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8466_285142_000002_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8466/285142/8466_285142_000002_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8466",
        "content": "There are long passages now before us of the most despicable trash, with no merit whatever beyond that of their antiquity..",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8466_285142_000002_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8466/285142/8466_285142_000002_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8466",
        "content": "The criticisms of the editor do not particularly please us.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8466_285142_000002_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8466/285142/8466_285142_000002_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8466",
        "content": "His enthusiasm is too general and too vivid not to be false.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8466_285142_000002_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8466/285142/8466_285142_000002_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8466",
        "content": "His opinion, for example, of Sir Henry Wotton's \"Verses on the Queen of Bohemia\"-that \"there are few finer things in our language,\" is untenable and absurd.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8466_285142_000003_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8466/285142/8466_285142_000003_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8466",
        "content": "In such lines we can perceive not one of those higher attributes of Poesy which belong to her in all circumstances and throughout all time.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8466_285142_000003_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8466/285142/8466_285142_000003_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8466",
        "content": "Here every thing is art, nakedly, or but awkwardly concealed.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8466_285142_000003_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8466/285142/8466_285142_000003_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8466",
        "content": "No prepossession for the mere antique (and in this case we can imagine no other prepossession) should induce us to dignify with the sacred name of poetry, a series, such as this, of elaborate and threadbare compliments, stitched, apparently, together, without fancy, without plausibility, and without even an attempt at adaptation.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8466_285142_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8466/285142/8466_285142_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8466",
        "content": "Walled about with disrespect; From all these and this dull air A fit object for despair, She hath taught me by her might To draw comfort and delight.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8466_285142_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8466/285142/8466_285142_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8466",
        "content": "Something more of this will be found in Corbet's \"Farewell to the Fairies!\" We copy a portion of Marvell's \"Maiden lamenting for her Fawn,\" which we prefer not only as a specimen of the elder poets, but in itself as a beautiful poem, abounding in pathos, exquisitely delicate imagination and truthfulness to anything of its species:",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8466_285142_000009_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8466/285142/8466_285142_000009_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8466",
        "content": "How exceedingly vigorous, too, is the line,",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8466_285142_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8466/285142/8466_285142_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8466",
        "content": "\"And trod as if on the four winds!\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8466_285142_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8466/285142/8466_285142_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8466",
        "content": "A vigor apparent only when we keep in mind the artless character of the speaker and the four feet of the favorite, one for each wind.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8466_285142_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8466/285142/8466_285142_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8466",
        "content": "\"And its pure virgin limbs to fold In whitest sheets of lilies cold,\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8466_285142_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8466/285142/8466_285142_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8466",
        "content": "and these things being its \"chief\" delights and then the pre-eminent beauty and naturalness of the concluding lines, whose very hyperbole only renders them more true to nature when we consider the innocence, the artlessness, the enthusiasm, the passionate girl, and more passionate admiration of the bereaved child-",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8466_285142_000014_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8466/285142/8466_285142_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8466",
